Roy Brunjes 
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
Various tools submitted together by the author.  StringPkg is string
package for both Forth style and NUL terminated strings.  Date&Time are
handy tools for getting and printing formatted date and time.  Utils are
utilities used by the other files.  CursorControl is an example of moving
the text cursor.  SpaceOrEscape is a handy word for pausing or stopping
program output.  Code.  
